attributes.review:
im going to start off by saying this app is probably the worst app in the entire app store. i open the app and start off by seeing this ugly orange faced man standing in front of the flag while looking up so you cant see his wrinkly saggy chin. i am disgusted and DEEPLY disturbed.

not only did i see that- but i also saw the saying “trump 2020” whAt on god’s green EARTH is that, i thought trumpet was dead or smth how can you vote a dead (racist, homophobic) person for president.

i was so petrified, i showed this app to my family and they all exploded because of how disturbing this photo is. now im an orphan and have NOBODY. i accidentally swiped on the app and it scrolls to this cheeto man’s NUDES and i get flashed with his pretzel d^ck. i was so horrified by the photo that i screamed and now i cant talk. my friends left me because their eyes popped out and they thought i was purposely looking at such a horrid picture. my cat even got BLINDED and died from shock bc of what she saw. my pet frog named jeffery is very disappointed and we both attempted to file a police report for the damage this app has done to my life.

finally after a long day of trying to contact the police (which didnt work bc they said they were too busy killing innocent POC for no reason) i went to bed. i was woken up by an alarm and looked at my phone.

i realized i forgot to delete the app. i frantically try to delete it but nothing works. suddenly my phone turns into a black hole and im sucked into the 4th dimension. i am now writing this review using my mind.

i hope everybody who sees this is warned so they dont download this app. stay safe ❤️
